description: Demolition of all existing buildings; redevelopment to provide 396 residential units (266 flats, 56 maisonettes and 74 dwellinghouses) in buildings ranging from 3 to 9 storeys; access from Grahame Park Way and Corner Mead; associated internal street network, open space, landscaping, parking refuse/cycle storage and amenity space provision; provision of 1.6 hectare site for educational use (subject to separate future planning application)
